                  <triggerstring n="disp">theilt</triggerstring>
                  <rs type="fn" role="recipient">dem <rs type="org" ref="org__wien">Bürgermeister,
                        Richter und Rathe zu Wien</rs></rs>
                  <triggerstring n="disp">mit</triggerstring>, dass er <rs type="fn" role="other"><rs type="person" ref="pe__johann_exelbegk_QGW_II_II_3742">Hannsen Exelbegkn,
